WEBVTT

00:01:27.240 --> 00:01:30.376
tukakuza ramani ya furaha mpya ya kitoto, 
kutokua na aibu ila ya hofu,

00:01:30.400 --> 00:01:32.656
tukajiita wanene na kumaanisha,
bila shaka,

00:01:32.680 --> 00:01:33.896
safi kabisa

00:01:33.920 --> 00:01:35.856
Mwaka huu, tulikuwa wanawake,

00:01:35.880 --> 00:01:37.656
sio bibi harusi au kishaufu,

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:39.176
sio jinsia duni,

00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:41.336
sio mawaidha, ila wanawake.

00:01:41.360 --> 00:01:42.656
Wafunze watoto wako.

00:01:42.680 --> 00:01:46.056
Wakumbushe kua mwaka wa kuwa
watulivu au wadogo umepita.

00:01:46.080 --> 00:01:48.696
Wale kati yetu waliosema ni 
wanawake kwa mara ya kwanza,

00:01:48.720 --> 00:01:51.096
kachukua kiapo hiki cha umoja kwa umahiri

00:01:51.120 --> 00:01:53.376
Kuna wale walizaa watoto na
wale hawakuzaa,

00:01:53.400 --> 00:01:55.816
na hamna miongoni mwetu 
aliuliza ilitufanyawakweli

00:01:55.840 --> 00:01:57.616
au sahihi au kweli.

00:01:57.640 --> 00:01:59.776
Anapokuuliza juu ya mwaka huu,

00:01:59.800 --> 00:02:02.705
binti wako, iwapo mwanawe au
mrithi wa ushindi wako,